imdb.plot outline: The show is about our Ancestors. That little voice that tells you, "don't walk down that street", "call your mom before she calls you", "take your umbrella..." but you don't listen and get caught in the rain. They are "Spirit guides" or "Ancestors",our protectors, or life guides. The show will show how frustrated they can get trying to do their jobs dealing with us humans, and the pros and cons to listening to them. This is a comedic show, that sometimes covers serious topics.
